      <title>中国敦促电动汽车制造商增加使用国产芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-15/china-urges-ev-makers-to-increase-use-of-local-chips-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府敦促电动汽车制造商增加从本土汽车芯片制造商的采购，以减少对西方进口的依赖。克雷格·特鲁德尔在彭博电视台进行报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-15/china-urges-ev-makers-to-increase-use-of-local-chips-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 11:22:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
